ont-size="12pt" font-weight="bold" font-style="italic" space-after="2pt" space-before.optimum="4pt" text-indent="0em">1.4. And now for something dramatic...</block><block text-align="justify" start-indent="1em" text-indent="-1em" space-before="3pt"><inline font-style="italic">Roderigo </inline><inline>Where shall we meet i' the morning?</inline></block><block text-align="justify" start-indent="1em" text-indent="-1em" space-before="3pt"><inline font-style="italic">Iago </inline><inline>At my lodging.</inline></block><block text-align="justify" start-indent="1em" text-indent="-1em" space-before="3pt"><inline font-style="italic">Roderigo </inline><inline>I'll be with thee betimes.</inline></block><block text-align="justify" start-indent="1em" text-indent="-1em" space-before="3pt"><inline font-style="italic">Iago </inline><inline>Go to; farewell. Do you hear, Roderigo?</inline></block><block text-align="justify" start-indent="1em" text-indent="-1em" space-before="3pt"><inline font-style="italic">Roderigo </inline><inline>What say you?</inline></block><block text-align="justify" start-indent="1em" text-indent="-1em" space-before="3pt"><inline font-style="italic">Iago </inline><inline>No more of drowning, do you hear?</inline></block><block text-align="justify" start-indent="1em" text-indent="-1em" space-before="3pt"><inline font-style="italic">Roderigo </inline><inline>I am changed: I'll go sell all my land.</inline></block><block keep-with-next.within-page="always" id="d25e462" text-align="left" font-family="Times" font-size="12pt" font-weight="bold" font-style="italic" space-after="2pt" space-before.optimum="4pt" text-indent="0em">1.5. Footnotes</block><block keep-with-next.within-page="always" id="d25e465" text-align="left" font-family="Times" font-size="10pt" font-style="italic" space-after="0pt" space-before.optimum="4pt" text-indent="0em">1.5.1. 1 Zur Entstehung der <inline>Philosophischen Untersuchungen</inline><footnote><inline font-size="7" vertical-align="super